292
00:16:50,710 --> 00:16:52,030
Please accept it.

293
00:16:58,830 --> 00:16:59,750
Okay.

294
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:02,790
Thank you.

295
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:07,060
