436
00:25:43,790 --> 00:25:45,700
Don't drop the ball later.

437
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:47,670
Come.

438
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,820
Come here, put this on.

439
00:25:57,030 --> 00:25:58,190
Listen,

440
00:25:58,430 --> 00:26:00,430
come to me

441
00:26:00,430 --> 00:26:02,350
