473
00:28:05,470 --> 00:28:06,950
Don't wait for me.

474
00:28:08,180 --> 00:28:09,710
Let me help you look for it.

475
00:28:10,870 --> 00:28:12,070
It's okay.

476
00:28:13,670 --> 00:28:14,750
Why don't you

477
00:28:15,110 --> 00:28:16,510
